        "tokenizer": AutoTokenizer,
        "pipeline": ImageTextToTextPipeline,
        "model": AutoModelForImageTextToText,
        "processor": AutoProcessor,
        "default": {
            "model": "onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft",
        },
        "type": "multimodal",
    },
```

**Design rationale:**
- `"tokenizer": AutoTokenizer` -- needed for tokenizing the text prompt and decoding outputs.
- `"model": AutoModelForImageTextToText` -- the correct auto model class that maps to LLaVA, Florence-2, Qwen2-VL, etc.
- `"processor": AutoProcessor` -- needed for image preprocessing (extracting pixel_values).
- `"type": "multimodal"` -- consistent with `"image-to-text"` and `"document-question-answering"` which also combine image + text modalities.
- `"default": { "model": "onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft" }` -- the requested default model.

